into one big document.
        
Please check the User Guide by clicking the Help button for usage instructions.
        
To get started, click on the "Next" button.
    </system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="ModifyMappings">Modify Mappings</system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="TemplateSelectionBlurb" xml:space="preserve">Select the folder where all of the Word Document templates are kept for each IO Type.
        
When the tool runs, the template will be selected based on the value of the column
selected in the previous step.
    </system:String>
    <system:String x:Key="TemplateSelectionLabel">Template Folder:</system:String>
</ResourceDictionary>